- Don't touch me!

49:11.616 --> 49:13.248
- We didn't need her anymore.

49:13.367 --> 49:14.700
She was going to get
in the way.

49:14.785 --> 49:16.418
- Oh, my god.

49:16.537 --> 49:22.424
