of those kinda people.

49:52.289 --> 49:53.789
I mean, gosh,
they come here like flies.

49:53.908 --> 49:55.791
- [coughs]

49:55.910 --> 49:56.659
- all right, look at me.

49:57.795 --> 49:59.628
