right here in front of you.

50:01.465 --> 50:03.799
Okay? Like, look,
my offer still stands.

50:03.918 --> 50:05.801
Come back with me to la.

50:05.920 --> 50:07.920
Could be a fresh new voice
in the visual arts scene.

50:09.924 --> 50:10.889
