of those creatures.

50:15.012 --> 50:16.145
- But you're not one of them.

50:16.263 --> 50:17.429
- [sighs]
- okay?

50:17.515 --> 50:19.598
You're talented.
You're a great painter.

50:19.684 --> 50:20.816
You're, like,
the next frankenthaler.

50:20.935 --> 50:22.317
- Oh, god.

50:22.436 --> 50:24.269
Oh, I'm cursed.

50:24.355 --> 50:26.321
I'm cursed!

