51:08.315 --> 51:08.947
- yes.
- Yeah?

51:09.033 --> 51:11.116
- Yes.

51:11.202 --> 51:12.785
- Create that painting.

51:12.870 --> 51:14.820
Now.

51:15.706 --> 51:18.123
See what you can do.

51:18.209 --> 51:19.625
You'll be amazed
at what's inside you.

51:19.710 --> 51:21.710
- [laughs]

51:21.829 --> 51:22.711
- you'll see.

51:22.830 --> 51:24.713
You'll see it's worth it.

51:24.832 --> 51:26.381
[chuckles]

51:26.500 --> 51:28.801
but first...

51:28.886 --> 51:29.868
You have to feed.

51:29.970 --> 51:36.425
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

52:07.007 --> 52:10.242
- [shouts]
- [screaming]

52:10.344 --> 52:14.179
<i> [ominous tone]</i>

52:14.265 --> 52:17.299
[groaning]

52:46.330 --> 52:47.329
- I know I always said
this family

52:47.414 --> 52:49.164
was the most
important thing to me.

52:49.250 --> 52:50.833
- [whimpers]

52:50.918 --> 52:52.167
- more important than anything.

52:52.253 --> 52:54.887
More important than--
than my work.

52:56.841 --> 52:57.923
But I think...

52:58.008 --> 53:01.093
- [breath shakes]

53:01.178 --> 53:03.262
- I think I used to say that
because it made me feel better

53:03.347 --> 53:05.430
about how...

53:05.516 --> 53:07.316
Unimpressive my work life was.

53:09.854 --> 53:11.403
I even talked myself into
believing it.

53:14.742 --> 53:16.525
It didn't matter that
I never hit it in hollywood.

53:16.610 --> 53:18.310
I was a family man first.

53:18.412 --> 53:21.313
<i> [dark music]</i>

53:21.415 --> 53:22.698
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

53:22.783 --> 53:24.199
but I wasn't.

53:24.285 --> 53:26.535
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

53:26.620 --> 53:28.670
and I should have been honest
