53:32.459 --> 53:33.458
I love you.

53:33.544 --> 53:35.961
And I'm so sorry
this has happened.

53:36.046 --> 53:37.262
But the truth is...

53:39.049 --> 53:40.966
Alma and ursula are right.

53:41.051 --> 53:45.637
